Промпт 2 — Feature-Targeted Deep Analysis

FEATURE-БЛОКИ (10 штук):

1. nl80211 Interface — driver_nl80211.c, netlink socket, commands, events
2. WPA2 4-Way Handshake — rsn_supp/wpa.c, EAPOL-Key message processing, PTK/GTK derivation
3. WPA3 SAE — common/sae.c, dragonfly key exchange, anti-clogging, commit/confirm
4. EAPOL State Machine — eapol_supp/eapol_supp_sm.c, IEEE 802.1X states
5. EAP Framework — eap_peer/eap.c, method selection, identity handling
6. EAP-TLS — eap_peer/eap_tls.c, TLS handshake within EAP
7. EAP-TTLS/PEAP — eap_peer/eap_ttls.c, eap_peer/eap_peap.c, tunneled methods
8. PMKSA Caching — rsn_supp/pmksa_cache.c, PMK lifetime, PMKID matching
9. Config & Control Interface — wpa_supplicant/config.c, ctrl_iface.c, D-Bus
10. OWE/DPP — common/dpp.c, DPP bootstrapping and authentication

